  "text": "The exclusion of publications that included study participants under the age of 18 resulted in the exclusion of the two studies that analyzed the autism spectrum disorders. [CITATION_1] 45 Autism spectrum disorders have not been assessed directly among younger adult premutation carriers. Although these excluded studies are not included in the body of the review, the possibility that premutation carriers are at an increased risk of autism spectrum disorders cannot be ruled out.",
